Highlights

   ECNL prepared a summary on the Report of the UN Special Rapporteur on
   the promotion and protection of human rights and fundamental freedoms
   while countering terrorism

   Call for submissions: “Soft law” and informal lawmaking in the global
   counter-terrorism architecture. Report GA 74th

   Joint letter of the Special Rapporteur to the relevant European Union
   organs in advancing full respect for human rights in regulation of
   preventing the dissemination of terrorist content online

   Letter of the Special Rapporteur to the UN CTED concerning pending
   review of the Madrid Guiding Principles

   The Special Rapporteur on the promotion and protection of human rights
   and fundamental freedoms while countering terrorism is one of the
   signatories to the Beirut Declaration and its 18 commitments on "Faith
   for Rights"

   Annual report of the Special Rapporteur, Fionnuala Ní Aoláinon, to be
   presented at the 73rd session of the General Assembly (A/73/361)

   Letter of the Special Rapporteur concerning Facebook’s overly broad
   definition of terrorism and the apparent lack of a comprehensive human
   rights-based approach to the policies governing access to and use of
   its platform

   Letter of the Special Rapporteur concerning the draft Counter-Terrorism
   and Border Security Bill, which is currently under consideration of the
   UK’s House of Commons (17/07/2018)

   The first report of the newly appointed Special Rapporteur, Fionnuala
   Ní Aoláinon, at the 72nd session of the General Assembly (A/72/495)

   Report of the Special Rapporteur at the 34th session of the Human
   Rights Council (A/HRC/34/61)

   The UN Expert on human rights and counter terrorism holds talks with
   the Government of Saudi Arabia to visit the Kingdom in early 2017 (20
   and 21 November 2016)

   Report of the Special Rapporteur at the 71st session of the General
   Assembly (A/71/384)

   Report of the Special Rapporteur at the 31st session of the Human
   Rights Council (A/HRC/31/65)

   HRC resolution A/HRC/RES/31/3

   Report of the Special Rapporteur at the 29th session of the Human
   Rights Council (A/HRC/29/51)

